Package: landtageAT
Title: Unified Access to Austrian State Parliament Data
Version: 0.2.0
Author: Fabian Habersack [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Fabian Habersack <fabian.habersack@gmail.com>
Authors@R: c(
    person(given = "Fabian", family = "Habersack", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "fabian.habersack@gmail.com")
  )
Description: Harmonized interface to discover parliamentary sessions and plenary
    protocols from Austria's nine state parliaments (Landtage), download source
    documents, and extract text where feasible. Uses state-specific backend
    adapters that prefer official structured sources when available and fall
    back to resilient HTML/PDF discovery with provenance metadata.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
