    dplyr,
    httr2,
    purrr,
    rvest,
    stringr,
    tibble,
    xml2
Suggests:
    pdftools,
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
Config/testthat/edition: 3
URL: https://github.com/example/landtageAT
